16 identified in subsection 1, paragraph M; after June 30, 2020 for employees identified
17 in subsection 1, paragraphs N to P; and after September 30, 2021 for employees
18 identified in subsection 1, paragraph Q; and after September 30, 2025 for employees
19 identified in subsection 1, paragraph R, then the member's service retirement benefit
20 must be computed in segments and the amount of the member's service retirement
21 benefit is the sum of the segments. The segments must be computed as follows:
22 (1) The segment or, if the member served in more than one of the capacities
23 specified in subsection 1 and the benefits related to the capacities are not
24 interchangeable under section 17856, segments that reflect creditable service
